<p align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:white">Clinical Action</span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p>
