<td style="border-bottom:1px solid #666666; width:24%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #666666; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Pruritus, hives limited to small area </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid #666666; width:28%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #666666; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Antibodies to transfused plasma proteins </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid #666666; width:30%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #666666; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Pause transfusion. Administer antihistamines. Resume transfusion if improved; NO samples necessary. If no improvement in 30 min treat as moderate to severe.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
