<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:24%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #666666; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection2"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Generalized hives<br/>
			(&gt;2/3 body surface),<br/>
